  {
    "number": 4,
    "title": "Episode 4",
    "overview": "With the addition of Caracal, Serval's group came to the An'in Region. There, the group heard an unbelievable singing voice and met Crested Ibis, the source of the song. She, too, was troubled by her own singing voice, so the group went to see an animal girl called Wise.",
