  {
    "number": 6,
    "title": "Episode 6",
    "overview": "The serval group succeeded in getting Crested Ibis to drink copaiba sap, but there was no change in her singing voice. On the contrary, the Celliens came closer. The fleeing group pushed the Celliens down to the bottom of the valley, but the Celliens crawled back up.",
